  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dive into the nostalgic world of classic coin pusher machines, now brought to life on your computer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop coins, trigger satisfying chain reactions, and watch piles shift, collapse, and spill over the edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This physics-driven arcade experience blends relaxing gameplay with addictive progression for fans of coin pusher and arcade games alike.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Mode:</strong> Race against time to collect rewards and clear the machine before time runs out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zen Mode:</strong> Relax and enjoy satisfying, low-pressure gameplay at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade Mode:</strong> Embrace the chaos with fast-paced gameplay, featuring minigames, power-ups, and dynamic events.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/c72df1715934a734d6c65cc9eeb31fb9.poster.avif?t=1774277000\" width=700 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/c72df1715934a734d6c65cc9eeb31fb9.webm?t=1774277000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/c72df1715934a734d6c65cc9eeb31fb9.mp4?t=1774277000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪙 <strong>Trigger satisfying physics-based chain reactions</strong> as coins pile up, shift, and cascade over the edge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎰 <strong>Take on 100+ unique levels</strong>, each with distinct layouts, challenges, and surprises</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙️ <strong>Enhance your gameplay with powerful perks and upgrades</strong> to boost your coin-dropping strategy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 <strong>Master timing and placement</strong> to maximize rewards and create massive coin drops</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>Discover integrated bonus mechanics and minigames</strong> built into each machine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧘 <strong>Relax and unwind</strong> with a satisfying, low-pressure arcade experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>Chase high scores and optimize your runs</strong> in addictive score-based gameplay</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/74465455fd35b7d498c1f95f304970bc.poster.avif?t=1774277000\" width=770 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/74465455fd35b7d498c1f95f304970bc.webm?t=1774277000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/74465455fd35b7d498c1f95f304970bc.mp4?t=1774277000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Highlights:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Satisfying Physics:</strong> Trigger chain reactions as coins pile up, shift, and collapse in motion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Arcade Charm:</strong> Relive the nostalgic feel of classic coin pusher machines with modern visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Constant Progression:</strong> Unlock new levels, machines, and treasure-filled rewards as you play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/294ce620e51b941f868dc01c3ee27c39.avif?t=1774277000\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join the Fun!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coin Pusher Casino is a relaxing, physics-driven arcade experience that captures the satisfying feel of classic coin pusher machines with a modern twist. Drop coins, build momentum, and enjoy the rewarding flow of cascading chain reactions.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dive into the nostalgic world of classic coin pusher machines, now brought to life on your computer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop coins, trigger satisfying chain reactions, and watch piles shift, collapse, and spill over the edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This physics-driven arcade experience blends relaxing gameplay with addictive progression for fans of coin pusher and arcade games alike.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Mode:</strong> Race against time to collect rewards and clear the machine before time runs out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zen Mode:</strong> Relax and enjoy satisfying, low-pressure gameplay at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade Mode:</strong> Embrace the chaos with fast-paced gameplay, featuring minigames, power-ups, and dynamic events.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/c72df1715934a734d6c65cc9eeb31fb9.poster.avif?t=1774277000\" width=700 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/c72df1715934a734d6c65cc9eeb31fb9.webm?t=1774277000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178590/extras/c72df1715934a734d6c65cc9eeb31fb9.mp4?t=1774277000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪙 <strong>Trigger satisfying physics-based chain reactions</strong> as coins pile up, shift, and cascade over the edge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎰 <strong>Take on 100+ unique levels</strong>, each with distinct layo